CustomField.description: BODEV-4335 DoA Refinement - Build: Partner Attributes This field is for Partner Sales team to manage Partner information. This is to capture the percentage of the referral fee that Bynder owes to Partner.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field indicates the % Bynder pays to the partner for closed won deals the partner sourced or the % of revenue share due. If the % can vary, the highest possible % is entered.
CustomField.label: Partner Fee % to Partner
